  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">Information Standards and Collections (including Extractions)</xref>
 are approved by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">Data Coordination Board</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">DCB</xref>).        </p>
    <p>
From 1 April 2017, the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">Data Coordination Board</xref>
 took over responsibility for the approval of 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">Information Standards and Collections (including Extractions)</xref>
 from the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_standardisation_committee_for_care_information">Standardisation Committee for Care Information</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
Further information on 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">Information Standards and Collections (including Extractions)</xref>
 can be found on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/information-standards/information-standards-and-data-collections-including-extractions" scope="external" format="html">Information Standards and Collections (Including Extractions)</xref>.        </p>
